  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SURVIVE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to Backrooms. In this liminal world, you must protect the outpost against various entities and most importantly, you have to survive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101910/extras/40c73794df4f5c7eaf869b1d373b9cd6.poster.avif?t=1732032175\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101910/extras/40c73794df4f5c7eaf869b1d373b9cd6.webm?t=1732032175\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101910/extras/40c73794df4f5c7eaf869b1d373b9cd6.mp4?t=1732032175\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >LIMITED RESOURCES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Watch your surroundings through cameras, keep creatures away by using lights, and protect yourself by locking doors in case of danger. But don't forget! The outpost's energy is limited and if you consume it you may have to face the entities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101910/extras/4cc3bdabdea7cf0c92d590fcffd3b5bf.poster.avif?t=1732032175\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101910/extras/4cc3bdabdea7cf0c92d590fcffd3b5bf.webm?t=1732032175\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101910/extras/4cc3bdabdea7cf0c92d590fcffd3b5bf.mp4?t=1732032175\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >TRADE WITH TRADERS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can buy tools from the shop with the money you earn. Or you can buy it at a reasonable price from traders who stop by the outpost at night.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101910/extras/05b0eb4a4dd8603857ee38830bd5eb4e.poster.avif?t=1732032175\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101910/extras/05b0eb4a4dd8603857ee38830bd5eb4e.webm?t=1732032175\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101910/extras/05b0eb4a4dd8603857ee38830bd5eb4e.mp4?t=1732032175\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SURVIVE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to Backrooms. In this liminal world, you must protect the outpost against various entities and most importantly, you have to survive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101910/extras/40c73794df4f5c7eaf869b1d373b9cd6.poster.avif?t=1732032175\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101910/extras/40c73794df4f5c7eaf869b1d373b9cd6.webm?t=1732032175\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101910/extras/40c73794df4f5c7eaf869b1d373b9cd6.mp4?t=1732032175\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >LIMITED RESOURCES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Watch your surroundings through cameras, keep creatures away by using lights, and protect yourself by locking doors in case of danger. But don't forget! The outpost's energy is limited and if you consume it you may have to face the entities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101910/extras/4cc3bdabdea7cf0c92d590fcffd3b5bf.poster.avif?t=1732032175\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101910/extras/4cc3bdabdea7cf0c92d590fcffd3b5bf.webm?t=1732032175\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101910/extras/4cc3bdabdea7cf0c92d590fcffd3b5bf.mp4?t=1732032175\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >TRADE WITH TRADERS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can buy tools from the shop with the money you earn. Or you can buy it at a reasonable price from traders who stop by the outpost at night.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101910/extras/05b0eb4a4dd8603857ee38830bd5eb4e.poster.avif?t=1732032175\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101910/extras/05b0eb4a4dd8603857ee38830bd5eb4e.webm?t=1732032175\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101910/extras/05b0eb4a4dd8603857ee38830bd5eb4e.mp4?t=1732032175\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
